les Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=20 May 2019|accessdate=5 July 2019}}\n* For \"Evil Spider\", \"Want Me Back\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/nzsingles?chart=4668 |title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=5 July 2019|accessdate=5 July 2019}}\n* For \"Kua Kore He Kupu / Soaked\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/nzsingles?chart=4746 |title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=14 September 2019|accessdate=14 September 2019}}\n* For \"Find an Island\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/nzsingles?chart=4766 |title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=26 October 2019|accessdate=26 October 2019}}\n* For \"Monsta\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/nzsingles?chart=4772 |title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=11 November 2019|accessdate=13 December 2019}}\n* For \"Glitter\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/nzsingles?chart=4792 |title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=14 December 2019|accessdate=14 December 2019}}\n* For \"Supalonely\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/nzsingles?chart=4838 |title=NZ Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=28 March 2020|accessdate=28 March 2020}}\n</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.75em;font-size:85%;\" | [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br /><ref>Peaks on the ARIA Singles Chart:\n* All except noted: {{Cite web|url=https://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Benee|title=Discography Benee|website=australian-charts.com|access-date=13 March 2020}}\n* \"Find an Island\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2019/10/aria-chart-watch-548/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #548|publisher=auspOp|date=26 October 2019|accessdate=26 October 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=6 April 2020|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.75em;